INSERT INTO public.tojung (id,num,total,jan,feb,mar,apr,may,jun,jul,aug,sep,oct,nov,"dec",created_at,nation) VALUES (360,'062','âœ¨ 1. 2026 Overall Fortune
The year 2026 is a glorious year when your name spreads in all directions and receives respect from everyone, like a bird returning to its nest and renovating it. As hundreds of flowers bloom competitively, there is light for thousands of miles, fortune is hopeful, and movement brings much profit. Life is peaceful and everything is achieved as desired in this fortunate year. Advancing north and south and pushing forward brings success, and wisdom is needed to know when to organize and pause even during great progress. However, this year lawsuits and disputes are unfavorable, so be especially careful not to get involved in conflicts. Never collude with corruption or illegal activities, and blessings will follow if you walk the honest and righteous path.

âœ¨ 2. ğŸ’° Wealth and Financial Fortune
2026 brings very robust financial fortune. With high spirits and nothing to envy, there are many extremely auspicious periods when wealth can be obtained at will. In January, harmony prevails above and below with extremely good financial fortune, so actively seize opportunities. Wealth lies outside, so external activities are favorable, and turning eyes to external work rather than household affairs brings great income. In April, business or investment toward the south is very auspicious, so push forward actively. In July and August, like fish and dragons obtaining water, vitality increases hundreds of times, making it the right time for large-scale investment or business expansion. In September, unexpected wealth is obtained like rain after drought, so maintain a grateful heart. In November, wealth is abundant and body comfortable as investments bear fruit. In December, unexpected success is achieved through benefactor help and blessings enter.

âœ¨ 3. ğŸ† Career and Promotion Fortune
Career fortune is a very bright year. As your name spreads in all directions and receives respect from everyone, actively promote yourself and demonstrate abilities. In March, there are celebrations at home and success comes from going outside, so you may receive overseas assignments, business trips, or new projects. West and north directions are especially auspicious for reference. In April, work toward the south is greatly auspicious and heaven helps everything proceed smoothly. In July and August, courage soars and vitality overflows, so challenge important tasks and seize promotion opportunities. In October, pushing work in cooperation with others brings considerable profit and achievements. However, acting independently and excessively may harm blessings instead, so don''t lose humility. Avoid matters related to lawsuits or legal disputes.

âœ¨ 4. â¤ï¸ Love and Marriage Fortune
Love fortune is a year of many changes. In January, meeting new people with aligned intentions brings joy, so singles can meet good matches. Actively participate in gatherings and accept introductions. In March, there are celebrations at home, making it a good period to consider marriage or engagement. Connections in west and north directions are especially auspicious. Married individuals may feel confused in relationships with spouses in June due to difficulty gauging advance and retreat, so communicate carefully. Questions may arise about whether to trust or doubt close people, but wrong judgment brings financial loss, so act wisely. In September, associating with wrong people can be harmful, so be especially careful about romantic relationships. In December, reconciliatory energy fills the home and families harmonize, making it a good period for strengthening marital relationships.

âœ¨ 5. ğŸ¥ Health Fortune
Health fortune is generally favorable but has several points requiring attention. In January, body and mind are comfortable with very good health condition. In September, body is strong and wealth abundant with overflowing vitality, so work harder on health management. However, avoiding overwork and stress while maintaining regular lifestyle habits is important. In November, there may be gossip, so pay attention to stress management along with careful speech. Being excessively greedy or pushing work forcefully can harm health, so keeping to your place and living comfortably is recommended. Appropriate exercise, sufficient sleep, and balanced meals are secrets to maintaining health. Overall a healthy year, but avoid excessive greed and listen to body signals.

âœ¨ 6. ğŸ‘¥ Relationship Fortune
